# GhostPay - Confidential Web3 Payroll

GhostPay is a confidential payroll platform designed to solve the massive privacy issues surrounding public on-chain salaries in Web3. By leveraging **iExec Nox and Confidential Tokens (ERC-7984)**, GhostPay allows employers to stream payments, while employee balances and transactions remain completely hidden. Enhanced with an integrated **ChainGPT AI chatbot**, employees can query their balances and request advances seamlessly.

This plan details the technical architecture and implementation steps to build the application end-to-end within the time constraints of the Vibe Coding Challenge.

